        <ul class="list-disc pl-6">
          <li>The Service will be uninterrupted or error-free</li>
          <li>The information provided is accurate or complete</li>
          <li>Listed packages are safe, secure, or fit for any purpose</li>
          <li>The Service will meet your specific requirements</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="mt-4">
          YOU USE PACKAGES LISTED ON THIS REGISTRY AT YOUR OWN RISK. Always review code and licenses before using any software in your projects.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-8">
